name: Goobercoin #2
description:
All profits are split between filmmaker and skater. 
This clip features my friend Anderson, who is from the favelas of Brazil and grinds hard in America in pursuit of his dream of going pro. 

This trick was filmed at the Embarcadero Center in San Francisco on a cloudy, chilly Winter day. This spot is extremely historic and played a fundamental role in the development of modern street skateboarding.
